[
  {
    "startTime": 0.66,
    "endTime": 1.3679999999999999,
    "text": "♪♪♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 1.501,
    "endTime": 2.0999999999999996,
    "text": "Later!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 2.135,
    "endTime": 2.702,
    "text": "Hey!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 2.836,
    "endTime": 4.3709999999999996,
    "text": "Huh?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 4.504,
    "endTime": 7.974,
    "text": "My Spidey sense tells me there's something going on down there."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 7.974,
    "endTime": 10.343,
    "text": "[grunts] Everything OK?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 10.477,
    "endTime": 14.814,
    "text": "That boy wants to swing, but if I give up my turn, he'll never let me back on."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 14.814,
    "endTime": 16.583,
    "text": "Did you ask him to share the swing with you?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 16.716,
    "endTime": 19.686,
    "text": "He looks like he might be mean and wouldn't share with me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 19.686,
    "endTime": 21.688,
    "text": "You'll never know if you don't at least talk to him."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 21.9,
    "endTime": 27.299999999999997,
    "text": "This reminds me of a little mystery Captain Marvel and I had to unravel when we came upon a space alien with a problem."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 30.7,
    "endTime": 32.265,
    "text": "[grunt] Something going on Captain Marvel?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 32.399,
    "endTime": 34.801,
    "text": "I'm investigating a crashed alien spaceship."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 34.934,
    "endTime": 38.379999999999995,
    "text": "Whoa! There's the spaceship, but where's the alien?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 38.171,
    "endTime": 40.106,
    "text": "Look! It's an alien!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 40.24,
    "endTime": 41.908,
    "text": "Oh! That was easier than I thought it'd be."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 43.41,
    "endTime": 44.244,
    "text": "Run!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 44.377,
    "endTime": 46.846000000000004,
    "text": "[screams]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 46.98,
    "endTime": 47.946,
    "text": "What's going on?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 48.2,
    "endTime": 50.160000000000004,
    "text": "Glad you're here Captain Marvel, Spidey."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 50.15,
    "endTime": 52.9,
    "text": "A creepy-looking monster stole all our sugar."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 52.9,
    "endTime": 56.823,
    "text": "Then he threw green slime on the counter and now it's all over the place."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 58.24,
    "endTime": 58.925000000000004,
    "text": "[sniff]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 59.2,
    "endTime": 60.727000000000004,
    "text": "No toxic fumes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 60.86,
    "endTime": 62.961,
    "text": "I don't think it's dangerous, just slippery."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 63.2,
    "endTime": 65.298,
    "text": "Maybe we can spot the alien from up high."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 66.366,
    "endTime": 67.2,
    "text": "See it?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 67.333,
    "endTime": 68.268,
    "text": "[sigh] No, not yet!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 69.269,
    "endTime": 70.67,
    "text": "[alien grunts]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 70.804,
    "endTime": 72.72,
    "text": "What is that thing?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 73.306,
    "endTime": 74.673,
    "text": "[gurgling]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 76.676,
    "endTime": 77.877,
    "text": "[tire screech]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 78.11,
    "endTime": 79.813,
    "text": "Whoa! Something's wrong with that truck!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 79.946,
    "endTime": 80.48,
    "text": "Help!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 80.613,
    "endTime": 81.481,
    "text": "[scream]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 81.614,
    "endTime": 83.316,
    "text": "You get the people; I'll get the truck!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 87.187,
    "endTime": 90.2,
    "text": "This alien is stealing sugar everywhere he goes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 90.223,
    "endTime": 93.126,
    "text": "And what's with leaving green slime all over the place?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 93.259,
    "endTime": 94.961,
    "text": "Guess we'll find out once we catch him."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 95.2,
    "endTime": 96.663,
    "text": "Where else could he get a lot of sugar?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 96.8,
    "endTime": 98.0,
    "text": "The cotton candy vendor!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 98.1,
    "endTime": 100.69999999999999,
    "text": "She's right near his crashed spaceship!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 100.834,
    "endTime": 102.735,
    "text": "[kids playing]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 102.869,
    "endTime": 104.237,
    "text": "[alien grunts]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 104.37,
    "endTime": 105.638,
    "text": "[gasp]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 105.772,
    "endTime": 107.40700000000001,
    "text": "Aahh!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 107.54,
    "endTime": 108.70800000000001,
    "text": "That's him!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 108.842,
    "endTime": 110.176,
    "text": "[grunts]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 110.31,
    "endTime": 112.745,
    "text": "I think your sugar- stealing days are done!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 112.879,
    "endTime": 116.41600000000001,
    "text": "[alien grunts]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 116.549,
    "endTime": 117.75,
    "text": "[beep]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 117.884,
    "endTime": 121.87,
    "text": "Oops, sorry, I thought my translator was on."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 121.221,
    "endTime": 122.21000000000001,
    "text": "Whoa!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 122.155,
    "endTime": 124.19,
    "text": "I didn't steal anything."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 124.324,
    "endTime": 127.259,
    "text": "I paid for all these with this."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 127.393,
    "endTime": 130.597,
    "text": "Wait, you think you paid for it with the green slime?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 130.729,
    "endTime": 134.86800000000002,
    "text": "Yes, it's very valuable on my planet."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 135.0,
    "endTime": 137.403,
    "text": "Well, here it just makes a giant mess."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 137.537,
    "endTime": 138.905,
    "text": "And it's kinda creepy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 139.38,
    "endTime": 141.774,
    "text": "Oh! I didn't realize."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 141.908,
    "endTime": 143.70899999999997,
    "text": "I apologize for the mess."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 143.843,
    "endTime": 146.446,
    "text": "And for scaring anyone."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 146.579,
    "endTime": 147.547,
    "text": "Oh, I see!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 147.68,
    "endTime": 150.15,
    "text": "Just an inter-planetary misunderstanding."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 150.283,
    "endTime": 157.857,
    "text": "I'm very sorry about that, but I have to get these to my ship and fuel up for my trip home."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 157.991,
    "endTime": 159.15900000000002,
    "text": "With sugar?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 159.292,
    "endTime": 162.61,
    "text": "Yes! Sugar is what my ship runs on."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 162.195,
    "endTime": 165.932,
    "text": "I promise I'll replace what I took on my next visit."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 166.2,
    "endTime": 168.535,
    "text": "Sugar as fuel...interesting."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 168.668,
    "endTime": 173.6,
    "text": "Yeah. He seems scary, but he's just a guy who needs to get back home."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 173.139,
    "endTime": 174.5,
    "text": "[chirp/engine startup]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 174.5,
    "endTime": 176.776,
    "text": "Maybe we should give him a hand fueling up his ship."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 176.91,
    "endTime": 177.677,
    "text": "Sweet!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 179.212,
    "endTime": 184.951,
    "text": "So, you see, we thought Miek was a really nasty character until we talked to him. Why don't you try that?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 186.719,
    "endTime": 191.15699999999998,
    "text": "Um, hi! Would you like to take turns so I can swing too?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 191.291,
    "endTime": 196.196,
    "text": "Sure. I was going to ask you, but I thought you looked kinda... mean."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 196.329,
    "endTime": 197.66400000000002,
    "text": "[giggle]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 197.797,
    "endTime": 201.0,
    "text": "You know, you might not want to judge someone before you know them."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 201.134,
    "endTime": 205.90499999999997,
    "text": "Let me tell you about the time my friend Captain Marvel and I ran into Miek, a space alien."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 206.0,
    "endTime": 209.274,
    "text": "Oh, you'll like this story, it's a good one! [giggle]"
  }
]